DESCRIPTION:Sip\, sketch\, and let the creativity flow at our lively Drink 
	& Draw! With a live model and all art supplies provided\, all you have to 
	do is show up\, grab a drink\, and dive in. Expect great energy and a fun\
	, no-pressure space to create\, connect\, and enjoy the vibe—no experience
